it's going to be giving off a

00:04:55.500 --> 00:05:00.720
proton, but given the p h of
the enzyme in the body and

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:03.050
given the p k a, it wouldn't
be pronated.

00:05:03.050 --> 00:05:05.000
So how is it going to give off
something it's not going to

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:07.990
have. So these are the kinds of
questions people talk about

00:05:07.990 --> 00:05:11.320
in biochemistry, and if you're
in a biochemistry seminar and

00:05:11.320 --> 00:05:13.182
