00:19:50.150 --> 00:19:56.640
And so, oxidation number for
oxygen here, minus 2.

00:19:56.640 --> 00:20:00.890
The overall charge on
that is minus 2.

00:20:00.890 --> 00:20:04.590
So you have to figure out what
the math equals there.

00:20:04.590 --> 00:20:08.280
And so, if you run through the
