00:31:23.060 --> 00:31:25.790
All right, so what is an
electric chemical cell.

00:31:25.790 --> 00:31:30.000
It's any device in which
electric current, which is a

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:35.630
flow of electrons through a
circuit, is either produced by

00:31:35.630 --> 00:31:39.470
a spontaneous reaction, or
used to bring about a

00:31:39.470 --> 00:31:41.780
non-spontaneous reaction.

00:31:41.780 --> 00:31:44.530
And so a battery is technically
a collection of

00:31:44.530 --> 00:31:49.090
cells in a series, so that the
voltage that each cell

00:31:49.090 --> 00:31:52.905
produces is the sum, the battery
has the sum of the

00:31:52.905 --> 00:31:55.640
